{"word":"G1987 - ἐπίσταμαι - epístamai - ep-is'-tam-ahee - Know","slug":"G1987","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπίσταμαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>epístamai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ep-is'-tam-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Know"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - epistamai</b> - <i>ep-is'-tam-ahee</i><p/>Apparently a middle voice of <a href=\"#/G2186\">G2186</a> (with <a href=\"#/G3563\">G3563</a> implied); to <i>put</i> the mind <i>upon</i>, that is, <i>comprehend</i>, or <i>be acquainted with:</i> - know, understand."}]}